# brainstorm-toolkit cheatsheet

Printable one-pager. Lives at the repo root after `setup.sh` runs. Edit
freely — `setup.sh` skips this file once it exists, so your customizations
survive plugin upgrades.

For the **always-current** view of installed skills, run `/cheatsheet` —
it reads the SKILL.md frontmatter directly and never goes stale. This file
is the *map*; `/cheatsheet` is the *menu*.

---

## Pipeline at a glance

```
                ┌─────────────────────────┐
                │       /brainstorm       │  ← idea, no plan yet
                └────────────┬────────────┘
                             ▼
                  plans/brainstorm-*.md
                             │
       ┌─────────────────────┼──────────────────────┐
       ▼                     ▼                      ▼
   /pbi "..."            /sdlc {plan}            /task "..."
   (bounded               (autonomous              (single-row
   single PBI)            plan-to-PR)              TDD task)
       │                     │                      │
       └──────┬──────────────┘                      │
              ▼                                     ▼
        plans/pbi-NNN-*.md                    inline TDD
              │                                     │
              ▼                                     │
        /sdlc {pbi-plan}                            │
              │                                     │
              └──────────────┬─────────────────────┘
                             ▼
                            PR
                             │
                          merged
                             │
                             ▼
                  /post-deploy-verify
                  (pipeline profile)
```

In parallel, runnable any time:

```
  /repo-health      → scored sweep, prints the highest-impact next command
  /dead-code-review → deeper, multi-agent unused-code scan
  /flowsim {plan}   → trace claimed flows through code, flag drift
  /gotcha "<entry>" → capture a hard-won pitfall
```

---

## Top 10 commands

| Command | What it does | When |
|---|---|---|
| `/cheatsheet` | Print this map + every installed skill | "remind me what's here" |
| `/brainstorm [topic]` | Conversational ideation → plan file | start of any feature |
| `/sdlc {plan}` | Autonomous plan-to-PR pipeline | plan is bounded + clear |
| `/task "..."` | One-row TDD task | a single bug or small change |
| `/repo-health` | Hygiene sweep + score | weekly, or pre-release |
| `/test-check` | Run tests + log audit | before shipping |
| `/flowsim {plan}` | Plan-vs-code drift check | post-merge sanity |
| `/gotcha "..."` | Append a project pitfall | after a bug bites |
| `/repo-onboarding` | Regenerate AGENTS.md / project.json | new repo intake |
| `/dead-code-review` | Multi-agent unused-code scan | pre-cleanup, monthly |

