## Profiles

| Profile | Includes | Use when |
|---|---|---|
| `core` (default) | brainstorm, sdlc, task, status, repo-health, test-check, flowsim, gotcha, repo-onboarding, dead-code-review, eval-harness, e2e-loop, cheatsheet, knowledge skills | local dev — single-developer or small-team workflow |
| `pipeline` | post-deploy-verify, future brd-ingest / pbi-decompose / approve / deploy / monitor / rollback / coverage | enterprise pipeline with BRD intake, approval gates, deployment skills |
| `both` | everything | dogfooding the toolkit; mixed environments |

Re-run `setup.sh --profile <name>` from the plugin root to switch.

