## Config files (all optional, all gitignored or user-owned)

| File | Owner | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `AGENTS.md` / `CLAUDE.md` | You | Repo-wide agent instructions. Skip-on-exist; setup.sh writes a template only on first install. |
| `TASKS.md` | You | Portable task tracker (markdown checkboxes). Toolkit reads but never overwrites. |
| `GOTCHAS.md` | You | Project-specific pitfalls. `/gotcha` appends; you curate. |
| `.claude/project.json` | You | Test commands, log audit, eval runner, modules list. Every key optional; skills skip gracefully when absent. |
| `.claude/pipeline/<slug>/` | Toolkit | `/sdlc` run journals (run.json + per-stage sidecars). Gitignored. |
| `.claude/.next-action` | Toolkit | Optional next-command hint file for repos that wire in Stop-hook support. Gitignored when setup.sh creates the ignore entry. |

